### Movie Recommendation System

Have you ever wondered how streaming platforms suggest movies you might like? This project implements a basic content-based 
recommendation system. It uses Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques to analyze movie descriptions and recommend similar
titles based on user preferences.

## Key Skills:

-Using TF-IDF Vectorizer to convert text data into vectors.
-Calculating Cosine Similarity to find relationships between data points.
-Building a recommendation engine from scratch.

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- TF-IDF Vectorizer
- Cosine Similarity
